* [`DELETE /users/{user_id}`](/api/deactivate-user): Added new
  parameter `is_spammer` for marking as spam while deactivating a user.
* [`DELETE /users/{user_id}`](/api/deactivate-user): Added new
  parameter `actions` for performing actions related to deactivating
  users. Currently, this parameter only performs the action of
  deleting the messages of the user being deactivated and the bots
  owned by them.
